remarks.para:
Here the property Name, CellsStr and ElimsStr should be implemented before the property invoked, you should creates those 3 properties, returns the corresponding correct string result, makes them or and marks the attribute to help the code analyzer (if the code analyzer is available). The recommended implementation pattern is:
[FormatItem] private string CellsStr { [MethodImpl(MethodImplOptions.AggressiveInlining)] get => Cells.ToString(); }
You can use the code snippet fitem to create the pattern, whose corresponding file is added into the required/vssnippets folder. For more information, please open the markdown file README.md in the required folder to learn more information.
